section.div: This code shows an algorithm for importing and mapping 2D images to 3D plots. Mapping algorithm: maps 2D binary image to 3D form by transforming relative pixel color to depth.
A program for quick X-Ray Diffraction (XRD) pattern visualization. Now with crystallite size calculation using Scherrer equation.
